This is the tutorial project from the book http://www.amazon.com/Beginning-Django-Ecommerce-Experts-Development/dp/1430225351
All credit goes to the author

Dependencies:
    Python Imaging Library (PIL) or Pillow

Additional Notes:
Fill in the database settings in project's settings.py file and type in your login id and pass for Authorize.net transactions.
Authorize.net specific settings are:
AUTHNET_POST_URL, AUTHNET_POST_PATH, AUTHNET_LOGIN and AUTHNET_KEY 

